  "subject": "[AAI] Bump up api versions in aai-resources to the latest version (V24)",
  "commit_message": "[AAI] Bump up api versions in aai-resources to the latest version (V24)\n\nIn aai-resources folder, the latest supported version of AAI API was\nstill v21, this change appends the recent AAI version: v22, v23, v24.\nThese new AAI versions are necessary for SDNC implementation and\nUUI usecase in Istanbul release.\n\nIssue-ID: OOM-2817\nSigned-off-by: Decheng Zhang <decheng.zhang@huawei.com>\nChange-Id: I9f9cc568117e4a7f74607a58069acdb4ab4e2f69\n",
